Quote:  instead of catching my usual bus to Misery Place, i'm sometimes tempted to hop on the one to Happy Valley. Though in reality Happy Valley is not a particularly desirable W ellington suburb , with convoys of rubbish trucks trundling through it on the way to the tip, the name conjures up a magical  place of great contentment.
